snippet.title: ROMANCE OF THE THREE KINGDOMS XIV - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Triumph over the land, take charge, conquer territories and fly your colors in the latest installment from the Romance of The Three Kingdoms franchise. Romance of The Three Kingdoms XIV is coming to PS4 and PC Early 2020.
